'''一溴化铟'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，由[[铟|铟]]和[[溴|溴]]组成。它是一种红色晶体，有着扭曲的氯化钠型晶体结构。<ref>Stephenson N.C., Mellor D.P. "The crystal structure of indium monobromide" Australian journal of scientific research A  3 (1950) 581-586</ref>一溴化铟可以由加热金属铟和[[溴化铟|InBr<sub>3</sub>]]而成。它被用作[[微波硫灯|微波硫灯]]的制作。在[[有机化学|有机化学]]里，它可以把α,α-二氯酮反应成1-芳基-丁烷-1,4-二酮。<!--这样翻译？原文在英文维基百科。--><ref>{{cite journal | author = C. Peppe and R. Pavão das Chagas | title = Indium(I) Bromide-Mediated Reductive Coupling of α,α-Dichloroketones to 1-Aryl-butane-1,4-diones | year = 2004 | journal = [[Synlett|Synlett]] | volume = | issue = 7 | pages = 1187–1190 | doi = 10.1055/s-2004-825591}}</ref>=与一溴化铟与卤代烷反应产生烷基铟卤化物<ref>{{cite journal | author = M. J. S. Gynane, L. G. Waterworth and I. J. Worrall | title = Oxidative addition reactions of group III metals in low oxidation states III. Reactions of indium monohalides with alkyl halides | year = 1972 | journal = [[Journal_of_Organometallic_Chemistry|Journal of Organometallic Chemistry]] | volume = 43 | issue = 2 | pages = 257–264 | doi = 10.1016/S0022-328X(00)81599-5}}</ref>和与NiBr络合物产生Ni-In键的氧化加成反应是已知的。<ref>{{cite journal | author = J. Weiss, T. Priermeier and R. A. Fischer | title = Reactions of Elemental Indium and Indium(I) Bromide with Nickel-Bromine Bonds: Structure of (η5-C5H5)(Ph3P)Ni-InBr2(O=PPh3) | year = 1996 | journal = [[Inorg._Chem.|Inorg. Chem.]] | volume = 35 | issue = 1 | pages = 71–75 | doi = 10.1021/ic950614i }}</ref>它和[[十羰基二锰|十羰基二锰]]发生{{le|插入反应|Insertion reaction}}，生成BrIn[Mn(CO)<sub>5</sub>]<sub>2</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic and Nuclear Chemistry Letters|volume=4|issue=4|language=en|date=1968-04|pages=201–203|doi=10.1016/0020-1650(68)80061-3|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0020165068800613|title=Insertion reactions of Mn2(CO)10 with SnCl2, InBr, and Ga2Br4|accessdate=2021-12-10|author=J. Hoyano, D.J. Patmore, W.A.G. Graham|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618145048/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0020165068800613}}</ref>它在水里不稳定，会歧化成金属铟和[[溴化铟|溴化铟]]。当二溴化铟溶于水时，会先变成InBr，形成红色溶液，然后很快分解。<ref>{{cite journal | author = R. Dronskowski | title = Ambient-Temperature Formation of Crystalline Indium Monohalides from Aqueous Media | year = 1994 | journal = [[Inorg._Chem.|Inorg. Chem.]] | volume = 33 | issue = 25 | pages = 5960–5963 | doi = 10.1021/ic00103a054}}</ref>

